  "logNo": "110158546980",
  "title": "&#39;경기도 어린이 박물관&#39; 나들이~",
  "addDate": "2013. 2. 1.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110158546980",
  "html_size": 189325,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110158546980\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110158546980\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p>가정주부는 &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>'내일 반찬은 뭘할까?' </p>\r\n<p>고민하고,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>두 아이의 아빠인 저는</p>\r\n<p>'이번 주말은 뭘 하고 놀아주지?'</p>\r\n<p>를 고민합니다. ㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>산과 들, 바다로&nbsp;돌아다니는걸 좋아하는데. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>겨울이라 야외활동에 제약이 생기면서</p>\r\n<p>할 수 있는게 별로 없네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그래서, 애들 엄마의 의견을 따라 </p>\r\n<p>용인. 경기도 어린이 박물관을 가기로 합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>두괄식으로.. 견해를 밝힌다면</p>\r\n<p>잠실의 삼성어린이박물관과 비슷하다. 입니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a11cafec60cd2c16.jpg\" width=\"509\" height=\"680\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 509px; rheight: 680px\" id=\"20130201_206/isuhani_1359694431359XXpQr_JPEG/IMG_0404.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a11cafec60cd2c16.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>사진을 많이 찍어주면 좋은데.. </p>\r\n<p>사진찍는게 익숙치 않네요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>이 사진은 다 놀고 나오면서 간판이 보이게 한장찍어야겠다 싶어서 찍었죠. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>손에 든 것은 기념품 샵에서 산 장난감. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>.</p>\r\n<p>암튼. </p>\r\n<p>외관은 이렇게 생겼습니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f94b624eedb8afdc.jpg\" width=\"473\" height=\"632\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 473px; rheight: 632px\" id=\"20130201_57/isuhani_1359694619048FSdm1_JPEG/IMG_3440.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f94b624eedb8afdc.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>소방차 놀이 하는 곳인데,</p>\r\n<p>소방관 옷과 소방차 운전대를 다른 친구들이 차지하고 있어서 스티커 놀이만 했죠</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5a0c41b3f387d1cf.jpg\" width=\"482\" height=\"644\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 482px; rheight: 644px\" id=\"20130201_260/isuhani_1359694619513HErqi_JPEG/IMG_3443.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5a0c41b3f387d1cf.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>아~ 어색해??</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5222199a06102d08.jpg\" width=\"484\" height=\"647\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 484px; rheight: 647px\" id=\"20130201_92/isuhani_1359694619967Iutls_JPEG/IMG_3445.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5222199a06102d08.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>사진 모델되는걸 어색해 하지 않는 둘째.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ea6943a6dd5038ef.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 990px\" id=\"20130201_53/isuhani_1359694770734jSbwG_JPEG/IMG_0341.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ea6943a6dd5038ef.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>둘째도 즐겁나봅니다.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2cdd58a2400833d7.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 990px\" id=\"20130201_25/isuhani_1359694771274jlEzd_JPEG/IMG_0343.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2cdd58a2400833d7.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>무우도 심어보고.</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/612bc05da677fad9.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 990px\" id=\"20130201_183/isuhani_1359694771684O55rO_JPEG/IMG_0346.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/612bc05da677fad9.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>감자도 심어보고</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b02987465a44610b.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 990px\" id=\"20130201_214/isuhani_135969477206745eFm_JPEG/IMG_0351.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b02987465a44610b.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>두더쥐(?)&nbsp;동굴도 들어가봤죠.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1층부터 3층까지 있는데</p>\r\n<p>(이번엔 부모의 체력 문제로&nbsp;2층까지만. -.-;)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>1층에는 소방차, 경찰차, 자연놀이 등이 있네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>--------------------</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2층으로 올라갑니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>큰애는 신이 났습니다. </p>\r\n<p>너무너무 재미있어 하네요. </p>\r\n<p>둘째는.... 졸려서 컨디션이 좋질 않아요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a3d0904e2cfb219a.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 990px\" id=\"20130201_188/isuhani_1359694918588HjcBA_JPEG/IMG_0357.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a3d0904e2cfb219a.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>우리몸에 관심이 많은 첫째.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3161771488dfa838.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 990px\" id=\"20130201_295/isuhani_13596949190970dO0B_JPEG/IMG_0361.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3161771488dfa838.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>뭘 해도 새침떼기. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/320e65334e30b855.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 990px\" id=\"20130201_70/isuhani_1359694919481k0vYD_JPEG/IMG_0364.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/320e65334e30b855.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>엑스레이 판독 중</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bcd6ef86c1677dcc.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 990px\" id=\"20130201_42/isuhani_1359694919848LL2hh_JPEG/IMG_0365.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/bcd6ef86c1677dcc.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>기다리다가 의사가운을 구해서 입고는 포즈를 잡습니다. </p>\r\n<p>이럴땐 꽤나 진지하죠 </p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2ee912e3da2bcc77.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 990px\" id=\"20130201_37/isuhani_1359694920759hS4At_JPEG/IMG_0378.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2ee912e3da2bcc77.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>물장난할때는 진지하지 않아요 ㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2층에는</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>몸이란 주제로 방이 하나 있고,</p>\r\n<p>그 옆에 물을 주제로 방이 있네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>우리몸에 대해서 이것 저것 구경하고,</p>\r\n<p>물 주제의 방에서는</p>\r\n<p>물장난 하느라 정신없습니다. -.-;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/40435f9c75bad925.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"735\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 990px\" id=\"20130201_24/isuhani_135969492142501DMe_JPEG/IMG_0386.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5F60824')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/40435f9c75bad925.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>두시간여를 놀고</p>\r\n<p>간식먹으러 들어갑니다.</p>\r\n<p>기념품가게에서 커피와 간식도 파네요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>나름 컨셉잡고 사진 찍히는 중인 둘째.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>둘째는. 물감놀이에 재미를 붙이고 있어서인지 다른 장난감들을 들었다 놨다 하다가, 결국 물감을 선택하네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>첫째는 첫번째 사진에서 보이듯.. 커다란 장난감 ^^</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>-----------------</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>경기도 어린이 박물관은. 서울 잠실에 있는 삼성어린이 박물관과 많은 부분이 비슷하더군요.</p>\r\n<p>다만, 경기도민은 50% 할인된다는게 장점.</p>\r\n<p>우리 가족은&nbsp;경기도민 아니라서 할인 안되니까. 다음에는 삼성어린이 박물관에 가는게 나을 것 같네요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
